column5: AFTER YESTERDAYS SLOW ACTION ON THE ICE I HAD TO CRACK THE PIN OUT AGAIN. WHAT A BEAUTIFUL DAY OUT. ALMOST FELT LIKE MARCH. NOT A NIBBLE TILL IT WARMED UP SOME IN THE AFT. WENT 3FOR5.  THAT SHOULD BE IT TILL NEXT WEEK. WIFES HOME  LOL LOOKIN AHEAD ON WEATHER NETWORK AND IT SAYS PLUS 4 ON THURS
